px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center py-4\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold text-xl\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-8\" aria-label=\"Main navigation\"><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a><div class=\"relative group\"><button class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition flex items-center\" aria-haspopup=\"true\" aria-expanded=\"false\">Mahsulotlar<svg class=\"ml-1 w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M19 9l-7 7-7-7\"></path></svg></button></div><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#portfolio\">Portfolio</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#process\">Jarayon</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz#faq\">FAQ</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"text-gray-300 hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 border-l border-gray-700 pl-4\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-gray-400 hover:text-white\" hrefLang=\"ru\" href=\"/ru\">RU</a><span class=\"text-gray-600\">/</span><a class=\"text-sm font-medium transition text-teal-500\" hrefLang=\"uz\" href=\"/uz\">UZ</a></div></nav><div class=\"hidden md:flex flex-col items-end space-y-1\"><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-white font-semibold hover:text-teal-500 transition text-sm\">+998 77 080 22 88</a><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-300 text-xs hover:text-teal-500 transition\">+998 97 480 22 88</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white p-2\" aria-label=\"Открыть меню\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"mobile-navigation\"><svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M4 6h16M4 12h16M4 18h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main-content\" class=\"pt-20\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Article\",\"headline\":\"O'zbekistonda biznes sovg'a etiketi: VIP tanlov\",\"description\":\"VIP sovg'ada xatolardan qoching: etiket, madaniy kontekst, status darajalari. Ekspert gidini o'qing.\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/uzbekistonda-biznes-sovga-etiketi\",\"image\":\"/images/blog/uzbekistonda-biznes-sovga-etiketi.jpg\",\"datePublished\":\"2026-03-03\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-03\",\"author\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"logo\":{\"@type\":\"ImageObject\",\"url\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/logo192.png\"}},\"mainEntityOfPage\":{\"@type\":\"WebPage\",\"@id\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/uzbekistonda-biznes-sovga-etiketi\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Graver.uz\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Blog\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"O'zbekistonda biznes sovg'a etiketi: VIP tanlov\",\"item\":\"https://graver-studio.uz/uz/blog/uzbekistonda-biznes-sovga-etiketi\"}]}</script><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><nav aria-label=\"breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-8\"><ol class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 text-sm text-gray-400 flex-wrap gap-y-1\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz\">Graver.uz</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li class=\"text-gray-600\">/</li><li class=\"text-gray-300 truncate max-w-xs\">O&#x27;zbekistonda biznes sovg&#x27;a etiketi: VIP tanlov</li></ol></nav><header class=\"mb-10\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight\">O&#x27;zbekistonda biznes sovg&#x27;a etiketi: VIP tanlov</h1><div class=\"flex items-center space-x-4 text-sm text-gray-500\"><time dateTime=\"2026-03-03\">2-mart, 2026</time><span>2<!-- --> <!-- -->daqiqa o&#x27;qish</span><span>Graver.uz</span></div></header><div class=\"mb-10 rounded-xl overflow-hidden\"><img src=\"/images/blog/uzbekistonda-biznes-sovga-etiketi.jpg\" alt=\"O&#x27;zbekistonda biznes sovg&#x27;a etiketi: VIP tanlov\" class=\"w-full aspect-video object-cover\" loading=\"eager\"/></div><article class=\"prose prose-invert max-w-none\"><p>O&#x27;zbekistonda sovg&#x27;a - qadimiy mehmondo&#x27;stlik kodining bir qismi. Biznesda esa u protokolga aylanadi: hurmat, chegaralar va maqsad. Bu maqola - sotuv emas, ekspertiza: qanday tanlash va nimadan qochish.</p>\n<h2>Madaniy kontekst: sovg&#x27;a nimani anglatadi</h2>\n<p>Sovg&#x27;a ko&#x27;pincha &quot;aloqa mustahkamligi&quot;ni bildiradi. Biroq biznesda u shaffof bo&#x27;lishi va noqulay vaziyat yaratmasligi kerak. Shuning uchun minimalizm, sifat va protokol - asosiy mezonlar.</p>\n<h2>5 ta &quot;to&#x27;g&#x27;ri&quot; belgi: sovg&#x27;a qanday bo&#x27;lsa yaxshi</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Sifatli va neytral (har kimga mos)</li>\n<li>Uzoq yashaydi (tez buzilmaydi)</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash chiroyli (unboxing)</li>\n<li>Tabrik qisqa va hurmatli</li>\n<li>Brend minimal (lazer gravirovka - ideal)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Status bo&#x27;yicha tanlash: protokol xaritasi</h2>\n<h3>Top rahbarlar</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>VIP setlar: soat, premium ruchka, desk set</li>\n<li>Ism/initsial gravirovkasi - eng toza personalizatsiya</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Bo&#x27;lim rahbarlari va decision-maker</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Termos/daftar set, aksessuarlar</li>\n<li>Sifatli, ammo haddan tashqari &quot;qimmat&quot; ko&#x27;rinmaydi</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Operatsion aloqalar</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Amaliy buyumlar: termos, organizer, vizitka qutisi</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash soddaroq bo&#x27;lishi mumkin</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Nimani bermaslik kerak: etik risklar</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Juda shaxsiy buyumlar (didga bog&#x27;liq)</li>\n<li>Bahsli mavzu yoki &quot;hazil&quot; suvenirlari</li>\n<li>Sifatsiz gadget/promo</li>\n<li>Soxta brendlar (reputatsion risk)</li>\n<li>Noaniq kelib chiqish (huquqiy risk)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Taqdimot va kommunikatsiya: sovg&#x27;ani qanday berish</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Taqdimot vaqti: uchrashuv oxiri yoki muhim bosqichdan keyin</li>\n<li>Tabrik karta: 1-2 gap, rasmiy ohang</li>\n<li>Qadoqlash: toza, brendli, ammo minimal</li>\n<li>Hisobdorlik: kompaniya ichida qayd (kimga, qachon, nima)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Buyurtma bermoqchimisiz?</strong> Telegram <a href=\"https://t.me/graveruz\">@graveruz</a> ga yozing yoki saytdagi shaklni to&#x27;ldiring.</p></article><section class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6\">O&#x27;xshash maqolalar</h2><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\"><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/b2b-hamkorlar-uchun-sovgalar-etiket-gid\">B2B sovg&#x27;alar: hamkorlar uchun etiket va tanlov</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Hamkor/mijozga sovg&#x27;a tanlang: status darajalari, taqiqlar, gravirovka. Toshkentda buyurtma qiling!</p></article><article class=\"bg-gray-800/50 rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-700 hover:border-teal-500 transition\"><h3 class=\"text-base font-semibold text-white mb-2 line-clamp-2\"><a class=\"hover:text-teal-500 transition\" href=\"/uz/blog/vip-sovga-goyalari\">Hamkorlar va mijozlar uchun 15 ta VIP sovg&#x27;a g&#x27;oyasi | Graver Studio</a></h3><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm line-clamp-2\">Hamkorlar va VIP mijozlar uchun eng yaxshi sovg&#x27;a g&#x27;oyalari: premium gravyura, shaxsiylashtirilgan aksessuarlar va eksklyuziv to&#x27;plamlar.</p></article></div></section><div class=\"mt-12 border-t border-gray-800 pt-8\"><a class=\"text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-400 transition flex items-center\" href=\"/uz/blog\">← <!-- -->Blogga qaytish</a></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-black border-t border-gray-800 mt-20\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4\" href=\"/uz\"><div class=\"w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\"><span class=\"text-white font-bold\">G</span></div><span class=\"text-xl font-bold text-white\">Graver<span class=\"text-teal-500\">.uz</span></span></a><p class=\"text-gray-400 text-sm\">Toshkentda biznes uchun premium lazer o&#x27;ymakorlik va brendlash</p></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Navigatsiya</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz#services\">Xizmatlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/catalog-products\">Mahsulotlar</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/blog\">Blog</a></li><li><a class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\" href=\"/uz/contacts\">Aloqa</a></li></ul></div><div><h3 class=\"text-white font-semibold mb-4\">Aloqa</h3><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li><a href=\"tel:+998770802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 hover:text-teal-500 text-sm transition\">+998 77 080 22 88</a></li><li><a href=\"tel:+998974802288\" class=\"text-gray-400 h